					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Sprite DMA technically IS writes to $2004, they are just done by DMA.<br /><br />Reading from $2004 is however very ambigious. I think different revisions of the PPU are different, some allow reading OAM, some don't.<br />Anyway I see no valid reason to ever read OAM, to be honest.</div>

